\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Acceptably done.\u8221\'94 The Guide commented from beside him.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The remainder of the evaluation cycle went much the same as he spent the next few hours working his was through the course. After the second obstacle, which was a more advanced version of the first, with more poles offset from each other instead of in a straight line, the Guide began instructing him in some basic technique where his own attempts fell short. Until, finally, he gained the skill they were trying to impart.}
